w.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-fashion-environmental-impact-pollution-emissions-waste-water-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efast-fashion%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20heavily%20impacted%20the%20way%20she%20viewed%20her%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillie-eilish-barbie-song-dark-episode-what-was-i-made-for-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20Was%20I%20Made%20For%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20singer%20said%20that%20all%20she%20wore%20as%20a%20child%20were%20fairy%20dresses%20and%20skirts%2C%20even%20though%20she's%20now%20known%20for%20her%20baggy%20streetwear%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20wore%20pants%20or%20shorts%20when%20I%20was%20a%20little%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20Eilish%20told%20Complex.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20got%20to%20be%20about%2011%2C%20I%20got%20obsessed%20with%20this%20brand%20called%20Brandy%20Melville.%20And%20they%20only%20sold%20clothes%20in%20one%20size.%20I%20was%20chubbier%20and%20I%20was%20obsessed%20with%20these%20clothes%2C%20but%20I'd%20buy%20a%20shirt%20and%20it%20wouldn't%20fit%20me.%20That's%20when%20my%20body%20problems%20started.%20I%20was%20around%20the%20age%20of%2010%20or%2011.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillie-eilish-body-image-young-interview-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20went%20through%20puberty%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20slim.%26quot%3B%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20being%20in%20ballet%20further%20exacerbated%20her%20body%20image%20issues%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20wearing%20all%20these%20baggy%20clothes%2C%20and%20it%20was%20my%20style%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20was%20how%20I%20could%20feel%20comfortable%20in%20my%20body%20and%20not%20feel%20tied%20to%20how%20my%20body%20looks.%20I%20didn't%20want%20my%20body%20to%20be%20part%20of%20my%20outfit.%20I%20wanted%20my%20outfit%20to%20be%20my%20outfit%2C%20and%20my%20body%20happens%20to%20be%20inside%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Eilish%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrandy%20Melville%20is%20a%20popular%20clothing%20brand%20known%20for%20selling%20basics%20like%20crop%20tops%20and%20mini%20skirts%2C%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Bone%20size%20fits%20most%26quot%3B%20sizing%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20brand%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20claims%20regarding%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrandy-melville-teen-fast-fashion-racism-exploitation-hitler-marsan-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoxic%20and%20exploitative%20workplace%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20Brandy%20Melville%20employees%20told%20Business%20Insider's%20Kate%20Taylor%20that%20the%20company's%20top%20execs%20frequently%20discriminated%20against%20non-white%20employees%2C%20crossed%20professional%20boundaries%20with%20its%20young%20retail%20employees%2C%20and%20made%20sexist%20and%20antisemitic%20jokes.%20Brandy%20Melville%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20comment%20to%20BI%20in%202021%20in%20response%20to%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202022%2C%20the%20owners%20of%20Brandy%20Melville%20agreed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrandy-melville-15-million-settlement-class-action-lawsuit-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20%241.45%20million%20to%20settle%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20former%20workers%20that%20the%20retailer%20had%20violated%20California%20labor%20laws%20by%20forcing%20them%20to%20work%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20clock%26quot%3B%20and%20without%20breaks.%20However%2C%20they%20denied%20all%20wrongdoing%20in%20the%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Brandy%20Melville%20opened%20a%20sister%20store%20%E2%80%94%20named%20St.%20George%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Santa%20Monica%2C%20California%2C%20where%20some%20items%20are%20now%20available%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedium%26quot%3B%20size%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5