20his%20mental%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEx-armyman%20Rajesh%20Kumar%20(51)%2C%20his%20wife%20Komal%20(46)%20and%20their%20daughter%20Kavita%20(23)%20were%20found%20murdered%20at%20their%20house%20in%20Deoli%20village%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Tanwar%20did%20not%20have%20good%20relations%20with%20his%20parents%20and%20was%20upset%20that%20they%20liked%20his%20sister%20more%20than%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20he%20was%20produced%20before%20a%20city%20court%20from%20where%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20three-day%20police%20custody.%20The%20police%20said%20in%20the%20court%20that%20they%20have%20to%20interrogate%20him%20thoroughly%20and%20confront%20him%20with%20some%20people%20and%20other%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20investigation%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20accused%20had%20searched%20for%20kind%20of%20murder%20techniques%20on%20internet%20before%20committing%20the%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20seized%20his%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptop%20and%20other%20electronic%20gadgets%2C%20which%20will%20also%20help%20ascertain%20if%20he%20watched%20crime%20web%20series%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20to%20commit%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20contemplating%20to%20conduct%20his%20psycho-analysis%20test.%20This%20will%20help%20establish%20his%20state%20of%20mind%20behind%20the%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20recovered%20his%20blood-stained%20sweatshirt%20and%20the%20army%20knife%20from%20nearby%20Sanjay%20Van%20late%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20Tanwar%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20first%20killed%20his%20sister%20by%20slitting%20her%20throat%20while%20she%20was%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20went%20upstairs%20where%20he%20stabbed%20his%20father%20in%20his%20neck%20and%20slit%20his%20mother's%20throat%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20washroom%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanwar%20then%20changed%20his%20blood-stained%20clothes%2C%20put%20them%20in%20his%20gym%20bag%20and%20went%20to%20Sanjay%20Van%20where%20he%20dumped%20them%20along%20with%20the%20knife%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20back%20home%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20clean%20blood%20spots%20in%20the%20washroom%20and%20other%20articles%20in%20the%20house%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanwar%20then%20provided%20a%20false%20alibi%20to%20police%2C%20claiming%20he%20was%20at%20the%20gym%20when%20the%20family%20members%20were%20murdered%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20was%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20political%20science%20at%20a%20Delhi%20University%20college%20and%20was%20a%20trained%20boxer.%20He%20represented%20Delhi%20in%20a%20state%20boxing%20event%2C%20where%20he%20won%20the%20silver%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20previously%20studied%20at%20the%20Army%20Public%20School%20in%20Dhaula%20Kuan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20psycho-analysis%20tests%20were%20done%20on%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Swiss%20woman%20Nina%20Berger%20in%20west%20Delhi's%20Tilak%20Nagar%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20tests%20were%20done%20on%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%2016-year-old%20girl%20in%20northwest%20Delhi's%20Shahbad%20Dairy%20area%20and%20on%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20parliament%20breach%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20police%20also%20conducted%20a%20psycho-analysis%20test%20on%20Shradha%20Walker's%20murder%20accused%20Aftab%20Poonawala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733467020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ftdr6285_delhi-triple-murder_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%22%2C%