ow%2F116033787.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20faltered%20late%20in%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20second%20day-night%20Test%20against%20Australia%20in%20Adelaide.%20Mitchell%20Starc%20dismissed%20KL%20Rahul%20(37)%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20(7)%20in%20quick%20succession%2C%20while%20Scott%20Boland%20trapped%20Shubman%20Gill%20(31)%20lbw.%20India%20slumped%20from%2069%2F1%20to%2082%2F4%20at%20Tea%2C%20losing%20three%20wickets%20for%2012%20runs%20in%20the%20space%20of%2016%20balls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Fadnavis's%20Rise%20Will%20Have%20Repercussions%20Beyond%20Maharashtra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fs3uhpqj_devendra-fadnavis-_625x300_25_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20installation%20of%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20time%20is%20set%20to%20change%20the%20politics%20of%20Maharashtra%20forever%2C%20with%20repercussions%20far%20beyond%20the%20state.%20Following%20an%20unprecedented%20victory%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%2054-year-old%20leader%20has%20signalled%20that%20he%20has%20finally%20arrived.%20Unlike%20many%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20chief%20ministers%2C%20Fadnavis%20is%20not%20faceless%2C%20and%20that%20is%20his%20strength.%20Like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Fadnavis%20has%20shown%20that%20he%20is%20a%20leader%20in%20his%20own%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20is%20the%20fourth%20Chief%20Minister%20from%20the%20Vidarbha%20region%2C%20following%20M.%20S.%20Kannamwar%2C%20Vasantrao%20Naik%2C%20and%20Sudhakarrao%20Naik.%20As%20Home%20Minister%2C%20Fadnavis%20may%20not%20have%20used%20a%20bulldozer%2C%20but%20he%20took%20a%20tough%20stance%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20Bheema-Koregaon%20case%20and%20'urban%20naxals'.%20He%20insists%20that%20the%20slogans%20%E2%80%9CBatenge%20to%20Katenge%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CEk%20Hai%20to%20Safe%20Hai%E2%80%9D%20were%20calls%20of%20the%20hour%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20be%20apologetic%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20victory%2C%20Fadnavis%20has%20placed%20himself%20among%20the%20foremost%20leaders%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20alongside%20a%20select%20few.%20His%20rise%20has%20been%20supported%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20since%20he%20emerged%20on%20the%20national%20stage.%20Fadnavis%20has%20always%20been%20grateful%20and%20loyal%20to%20his%20leader%20and%20shares%20his%20tact%20and%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShiv%20Sena%20May%20Be%20The%20First%20Target%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Fadnavis%20firmly%20in%20control%2C%20observers%20believe%20that%20things%20will%20never%20be%20the%20same%20in%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20industrial%20states.%20The%20first%20target%20on%20his%20list%20could%20be%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20his%20party%2C%20as%20Fadnavis%20might%20soon%20order%20the%20long-delayed%20elections%20to%20municipal%20corporations%2C%20including%20Greater%20Mumbai%2C%20to%20further%20weaken%20the%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena.%20The%20old%20political%20principle%20of%20%E2%80%9Cstrike%20while%20the%20iron%20is%20hot%E2%80%9D%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20have%20been%20many%20claims%20and%20counterclaims%2C%20both%20formally%20and%20informally%2C%20but%20everyone%20who%20matters%20in%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20was%20convinced%20that%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20crown%20belonged%20to%20Fadnavis.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20of%20reckoning%20for%20the%20leader%20from%20Nagpur%2C%20who%20has%20consistently%20faced%20attacks%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20provocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Fadnavis's%20strengths%20as%20a%20leader%20is%20his%20ability%20to%20combine%20a%20soft%20face%20with%20hardline%20tactics%20and%20strategy.%20This%20approach%20has%20not%20only%20crushed%20his%20political%20opponents%20but%20also%20silenced%20detractors%20within%20his%20own%20party%20who%20either%20underestimated%20him%20or%20believed%20he%20could%20easily%20be%20marginalised%20because%20he%20is%20a%20Brahmin.%20While%20the%20Brahmin%20community%20may%20not%20be%20a%20dominant%20political%20force%2C%20it%20has%20traditionally%20done%20well%20in%20bureaucracy%20and%20other%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20BJP%20Dominate%20Maharashtra%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20is%20leading%20the%20state%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20opposition%20is%20either%20divided%20or%20has%20become%20faceless.%20He%20and%20his%20party%20succeeded%20in%20ensuring%20that%20Uddhav-led%20Shiv%20Sena's%20Hindutva%20claims%20remained%20diminished%20as%20it%20allied%20with%20parties%20like%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20parties%2C%20along%20with%20Prakash%20Ambedkar's%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20(VBA)%20and%20Raj%20Thackeray's%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%2C%20are%20in%20no%20position%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20under%20Fadnavis%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Marathas%2C%20the%20dominant%20community%20in%20the%20state%2C%20have%20become%20%E2%80%98softer'%20towards%20the%20BJP.%20The%20party%20has%20been%20accommodative%20and%20is%20no%20longer%20dominated%20by%20any%20single%20caste%20or%20group%20of%20castes%2C%20unlike%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20used%20to%20be%20a%20party%20of%20Marathas%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20known%20for%20its%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esahi%20disha%2C%20spasht%20niti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(correct%20direction%2C%20clear%20policy).%20Observers%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20inching%20closer%20towards%20becoming%20the%20most%20dominant%20political%20force%20in%20Maharashtra%20for%20years%20to%20come.%20The%20saffron%20sweep%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20helped%20the%20party%20expand%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unexpected%20collapse%20of%20Congress%20in%20the%20traditional%20stronghold%20has%20made%20matters%20easier%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%20Until%20Congress%20gets%20its%20house%20in%20order%2C%20regional%20parties%2C%20despite%20being%20weakened%2C%20remain%20the%20primary%20hurdle%20in%20the%20BJP's%20expansion%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExistential%20Threat%20To%20Many%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis's%20re-emergence%20poses%20existential%20threats%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%2C%20and%20the%20Congress.%20The%20BJP's%20prime%20objective%20is%20to%20make%20Maharashtra%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eshat%20pratishat%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(100%25)%2C%20meaning%20to%20expand%20and%20strengthen%20the%20party%20so%20that%20it%20no%20longer%20depends%20on%20allies%20and%20faces%20little%20resistance%20from%20its%20detractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Fadnavis%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Nitin%20Gadkari's%20status%20within%20the%20party%20and%20the%20government%20appears%20to%20be%20declining.%20Gadkari%2C%20a%20former%20BJP%20President%2C%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20bringing%20Fadnavis%20into%20politics.%20Fadnavis%20is%20a%20second-generation%20politician%3B%20his%20late%20father%2C%20Gangadhar%2C%20was%20an%20MLC%20during%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20tenure%20in%20state%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadnavis's%20rise%20has%20been%20meteoric.%20He%20began%20his%20political%20career%20in%20the%20mid-nineties.%20In%201992%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2022%2C%20he%20became%20a%20corporator%2C%20and%20five%20years%20later%2C%20in%201997%2C%20he%20became%20the%20youngest%20Mayor%20of%20the%20Nagpur%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sunil%20Gatade%20is%20a%20former%20associate%20editor%20with%20PTI.%20Venkatesh%20Kesari%20was%20an%20assistant%20editor%20with%20The%20Asian%20Age.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733466720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fs3uhpqj_devendra-fadnavis-_625x300_25_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffadnaviss-rise-will-have-repercussions-beyond-maharashtra-7184716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fadnavis's%20re-emergence%20poses%20existential%20threats%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20the%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%2C%20and%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffadnaviss-rise-will-have-repercussions-beyond-maharashtra-7184716%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Call%20For%20%26quot%3BExemplary%20Punishment%26quot%3B%20In%20Bangladesh%20After%20Attacks%20On%20Hindus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladesh%20Hindu%20Buddhist%20Christian%20Unity%20Council%2C%20the%20largest%20minority%20advocacy%20group%20in%20the%20country%2C%20has%20condemned%20the%20recent%20attacks%20on%20Hindus%20in%20the%20eastern%20Sunamganj%20district.%20In%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20council%20recounted%20instances%20of%20violence%20and%20called%20for%20swift%20government%20action%20to%20hold%20the%20perpetrators%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20release%20from%20the%20group%2C%20violence%20erupted%20on%20the%20night%20of%20December%203.%20More%20than%20100%20houses%20and%20businesses%20belonging%20to%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Manglargaon%20and%20Monigaon%20East%20Gunigram%20were%20allegedly%20attacked%2C%20looted%2C%20and%20vandalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20a%20temple%20was%20damaged.%20The%20council%20estimated%20the%20damages%20to%20exceed%201.5%20million%20Bangladeshi%20taka%20(over%20Rs%2010%20lakh)%2C%20noting%20that%20many%20minority%20villagers%20fled%20their%20homes%20out%20of%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20reportedly%20stemmed%20from%20allegations%20against%20Akash%20Das%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20Hindu%20villager%20accused%20of%20blasphemy%20for%20a%20Facebook%20post.%20Mr%20Das%20had%20already%20been%20arrested%20before%20the%20attacks%20unfolded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBangladesh%20Hindu%20Buddhist%20Christian%20Oikya%20Parishad%20strongly%20condemns%20and%20protests%20such%20communal%20attacks%20and%20immediately%20arrests%20the%20attackers%2C%20compensates%20and%20rehabilitates%20the%20victims%20and%20the%20attackers%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20press%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20demanded%20the%20government%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bexemplary%20punishment%26quot%3B%20for%20those%20responsible%20to%20deter%20future%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeightened%20Tensions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20events%20come%20amid%20rising%20tensions%20over%20the%20treatment%20of%20minority%20communities%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20arrest%20of%20Hindu%20spiritual%20leader%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20on%20sedition%20charges%20has%20amplified%20concerns.%20Mr%20Das%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20Sammilit%20Sanatan%20Jagran%20Jote%2C%20remains%20in%20custody%20despite%20calls%20from%20India%20for%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20have%20erupted%20outside%20the%20Bangladesh%20Deputy%20High%20Commission%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20other%20Indian%20cities%2C%20with%20political%20and%20religious%20groups%20voicing%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Bangladesh%20summoned%20Shikder%20Mohammad%20Ashrafur%20Rahman%2C%20its%20Acting%20Deputy%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20for%20consultations.%20Mr%20Rahman%20also%20joined%20the%20Bangladesh%20delegation%20for%20upcoming%20foreign%20secretary-level%20talks%20with%20India.%20The%20Bangladesh%20Assistant%20High%20Commission%20in%20Tripura%2C%20has%20suspended%20visa%20and%20consular%20services%20citing%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20reasons%26quot%3B%20after%20protesters%20breached%20the%20mission's%20premises%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladesh%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20summoned%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Dhaka%20to%20protest%20the%20vandalism%20at%20its%20Agartala%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYunus%20Government's%20Position%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20escalating%20criticism%2C%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20head%20of%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%2C%20has%20sought%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20of%20minority%20communities.%20At%20a%20meeting%20with%20religious%20leaders%20from%20various%20faiths%2C%20Yunus%20urged%20the%20need%20for%20accurate%20reporting%20and%20urged%20collaboration%20to%20bridge%20gaps%20between%20reality%20and%20media%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20establish%20a%20process%20for%20obtaining%20accurate%20information%20and%20holding%20perpetrators%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yunus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20reiterated%20that%20all%20citizens%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20regardless%20of%20faith%2C%20are%20entitled%20to%20equal%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Muslim-majority%20Bangladesh%20has%20reportedly%20faced%20over%20200%20attacks%20across%2050%20districts%20since%20the%20fall%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20Awami%20League%20government%20on%20August%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17334666600