%3DUTF-8%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Tata's%20death%2C%20Mr%20Naidu%20shared%20a%20tribute%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20hole%20that%20this%20friendship%20has%20now%20left%20with%20me%2C%20I%20will%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20trying%20to%20fill.%20Grief%20is%20the%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20love.%20Goodbye%2C%20my%20dear%20lighthouse.%E2%80%9D%20He%20accompanied%20the%20note%20with%20a%20photograph%20of%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733462640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2F4fas0f5s_ratan-tata-with-shantanu-naidu_625x300_20_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshantanu-naidu-embarks-on-new-chapter-after-ratan-tata-s-death-7183852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shantanu%20Naidu%2C%20the%20manager%20and%20confidant%20of%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20fresh%20chapter%20of%20his%20life%20after%20the%20billionaire-philanthropist's%20death.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20Keeps%20Repo%20Rate%20Unchanged%20At%206.5%25%3A%20How%20It%20Affects%20Your%20Loan%20EMIs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20(RBI)%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20(MPC)%20has%20decided%20to%20keep%20the%20repo%20rate%20unchanged%20at%206.5%25%2C%20marking%20the%2011th%20consecutive%20meeting%20where%20the%20key%20lending%20rate%20has%20remained%20the%20same.%20The%20move%20comes%20as%20the%20central%20bank%20grapples%20with%20persistent%20inflation%20pressures%20and%20an%20uncertain%20economic%20growth%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20made%20the%20announcement%20on%20December%206%2C%20with%20the%20decision%20arriving%20from%20a%204%3A2%20split%20within%20the%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20(MPC).%20The%20last%20hike%20happened%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20different%20types%20of%20loans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI's%20move%20to%20hold%20the%20repo%20rate%20steady%20has%20various%20implications%20for%20borrowers%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20loans%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Interest%20rates%20on%20home%20loans%20pegged%20to%20the%20repo%20rate%20will%20remain%20unchanged.%20Equal%20monthly%20instalments%20(EMIs)%20for%20existing%20home%20loan%20borrowers%20won't%20see%20any%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto%20loans%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBorrowers%20with%20auto%20loans%20tied%20to%20the%20repo%20rate%20can%20also%20expect%20their%20EMIs%20to%20stay%20the%20same%2C%20with%20no%20adjustment%20in%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPersonal%20loans%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20individuals%20holding%20personal%20loans%20linked%20to%20the%20repo%20rate%2C%20the%20RBI's%20decision%20means%20their%20EMIs%20will%20remain%20steady.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20borrowers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThose%20considering%20new%20loans%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20interest%20rates%20to%20stay%20in%20line%20with%20current%20levels.%20This%20stability%20could%20benefit%20potential%20borrowers%20who%20are%20assessing%20the%20cost%20of%20financing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20repo%20rate%20unchanged%20at%206.5%25%2C%20there%20is%20no%20immediate%20impact%20on%20existing%20borrowers'%20EMIs%20or%20new%20loans.%20This%20move%20provides%20predictability%20for%20borrowers%20while%20keeping%20monetary%20policy%20supportive%20of%20economic%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20announcement%2C%20RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20explained%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20maintain%20the%20rate%20was%20driven%20by%20ongoing%20concerns%20about%20inflation%2C%20particularly%20food%20inflation%2C%20which%20has%20yet%20to%20show%20signs%20of%20stabilising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20Das%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20despite%20these%20inflation%20concerns%2C%20there%20is%20a%20reason%20for%20cautious%20optimism%20about%20India's%20economic%20growth.%20The%20positive%20impact%20of%20favourable%20monsoon%20seasons%20and%20the%20anticipated%20resurgence%20in%20capital%20expenditure%20are%20expected%20to%20support%20economic%20expansion%2C%20providing%20a%20counterbalance%20to%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20high%20inflation%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fpolicy%2Frbi-mpc-meeting-das-and-co-keeps-repo-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-amid-inflation-growth-concerns%2Farticleshow%2F116028826.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI's%20stance%20has%20shifted%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98withdrawal%20of%20accommodation'%20policy%20seen%20earlier%20to%20a%20more%20%E2%80%98neutral'%20approach.This%20change%20indicates%20a%20cautious%20pause%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20aggressive%20pivot%20toward%20easing%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733462640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmmlln67_home-loan_625x300_07_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Frbi-keeps-repo-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-how-it-affects-your-loan-emis-7184299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20(RBI)%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20(MPC)%20has%20decided%20to%20keep%20the%20repo%20rate%20unchanged%20at%206.5%25%2C%20marking%20the%2011th%20consecutive%20meeting%20where%20the%20key%20lending%20rate%20has%20remained%20the%20same.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20South%20Korean%20president's%20party%20says%20he%20needs%20to%20go%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20that%20he%20tri