ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.yna.co.kr%2Fview%2FAEN20241206002900315%3Fsection%3Dnational%2Fpolitics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYonhap%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHan%20added%20that%20he%20was%20concerned%20Yoon%20would%20take%20more%20%26quot%3Bradical%26quot%3B%20action%20if%20he%20remained%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20local%20media%20that%20leaders%20had%20learned%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Yoon%20instructed%20the%20country's%20intelligence%20commander%20to%20detain%20politicians%20during%20martial%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Han%2C%20Yoon%20had%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Banti-state%26quot%3B%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoon%20had%20used%20the%20same%20term%20to%20describe%20his%20political%20rivals%20when%20he%20made%20his%20shock%20announcement%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20accusing%20South%20Korea's%20opposition%20of%20being%20affiliated%20with%20North%20Korea%20as%20justification%20for%20martial%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20declaration%2C%20made%20at%20around%2010%3A27%20p.m.%20Seoul%20time%2C%20was%20instantly%20denounced%20by%20Han%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20party%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-opposition-leader-martial-law-declaration-was-deepfake-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELee%20Jae-myung.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20summoned%20their%20party%20members%20to%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20where%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-martial-law-what-happened-how-stopped-president-yoon-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoted%20to%20lift%20martial%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20troops%20could%20enter%20the%20main%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20300-seat%20National%20Assembly%2C%20190%20members%20were%20present%20that%20night.%20They%20voted%20unanimously%20against%20Yoon's%20decision.%20Yoon%20lifted%20martial%20law%20at%20about%204%3A30%20a.m.%20local%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E