22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20Appoints%20David%20Sacks%20As%20White%20House%20%26quot%3BAI%20And%20Crypto%20Czar%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20late%20Thursday%20named%20former%20PayPal%20chief%20operating%20officer%20David%20Sacks%20as%20White%20House%20%26quot%3BAI%20and%20Crypto%20Czar.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wealthy%20tech%20entrepreneur%20will%20take%20on%20a%20newly%20created%20role%20advising%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20cryptocurrency%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDavid%20will%20guide%20policy%20for%20the%20Administration%20in%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20and%20Cryptocurrency%2C%20two%20areas%20critical%20to%20the%20future%20of%20American%20competitiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20will%20safeguard%20Free%20Speech%20online%20and%20steer%20us%20away%20from%20Big%20Tech%20bias%20and%20censorship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESacks%20will%20also%20lead%20a%20presidential%20council%20of%20advisors%20on%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20according%20to%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%2C%20whose%20wealth%20has%20been%20estimated%20in%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20is%20considered%20part%20of%20a%20so-called%20%26quot%3BPayPal%20Mafia%26quot%3B%20cadre%20of%20influential%20tech%20entrepreneurs%20that%20includes%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Peter%20Thiel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20was%20part%20of%20that%20company's%20founding%20era%20and%20members%20have%20thrown%20their%20clout%20behind%20conservative%20political%20policies%20and%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESacks%20backed%20J.D.%20Vance%20as%20Trump's%20running%20mate%20in%20the%20recent%20US%20presidential%20election%2C%20hosting%20Vance%20on%20his%20podcast%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20PayPal%20was%20bought%20by%20eBay%20in%202002%2C%20Sacks%20went%20on%20to%20help