t%20came%20to%20light%20following%20a%20complaint%20by%20a%20parent%20to%20the%20State%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20alleging%20a%20section%20of%20students%20had%20to%20undergo%20'clinical%20trials'%20in%20violation%20of%20relevant%20rules.%20Also%2C%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20prior%20permission%20from%20parents%20was%20not%20obtained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%201963%2C%20Vana%20Vani%20Matriculation%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20(VVMHSC)%20on%20the%20sprawling%20IIT-M%20campus%2C%20is%20run%20by%20a%20not-for%20profit%20trust%2C%20in%20which%20Director-IIT-M%20is%20the%20managing%20trustee%2C%20according%20to%20the%20VVMHSC%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%2C%20the%20IIT-Madras%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20a%20fact-finding%20committee%20was%20constituted%20to%20ascertain%20the%20facts.%20The%20initial%20preliminary%20study%20was%20conducted%20on%20August%2019%2C%202024%20at%20Vana%20Vani%20School%20to%20understand%20the%20feasibility%20of%20a%20cost-effective%20smart%20insole%20assembled%20using%20commercially%20available%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20clinical%20trials%20nor%20any%20medical-related%20device%20trials%20were%20conducted.%20Neither%20medicine%20nor%20stimulants%20were%20given%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20institute%20said.%20Furthermore%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20assembled%20smart%20insole%20was%20placed%20%26quot%3Binside%20the%20insole%20of%20students'%20shoes%20to%20study%20the%20ease%20of%20walking%20(the%20study%20lasted%20for%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%20for%20each%20student)%2C%20which%20had%20no%20contact%20with%20the%20human%20body.%26quot%3B%20Along%20with%20the%20assembled%20insole%2C%20a%20commercially%20assembled%20smartwatch%20was%20used%20to%20collect%20the%20data%20separately.%20According%20to%20the%20faculty%2C%20this%20was%20just%20a%20feasibility%20test%20and%20not%20a%20clinical%20trial%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20it%20may%20not%20require%20permission%20from%20the%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20found%20that%20no%20invasive%20procedures%20were%20performed%2C%20and%20no%20liquid%20or%20solids%20were%20administered%20to%20any%20of%20the%20students%20before%20or%20during%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20this%20has%20been%20viewed%20seriously%20by%20the%20school%20management%2C%20and%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%20has%20been%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20faculty%20of%20IITM%20was%20also%20warned%2C%20and%20administrative%20action%20was%20taken%20for%20not%20ascertaining%20that%20permission%20from%20parents%20was%20to%20be%20obtained%20before%20performing%20the%20feasibility%20study.%20The%20feasibility%20study%20was%20immediately%20stopped%20on%20the%20same%20day%20on%20August%2019%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733451780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F2m9e88g4_iit-madras_625x300_03_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fa-10-minute-study-on-school-students-by-iit-madras-team-starts-a-row-7180780%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20preliminary%20study%20by%20the%20IIT-Madras%20researchers%20on%20the%20students%20of%20a%20school%2C%20located%20within%20the%20premium%20institute's%20campus%20here%2C%20has%20stoked%20controversy%20and%20authorities%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20action%20has%20been%20taken.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fa-10-minute-study-on-school-students-by-iit-madras-team-starts-a-row-7180780%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20beats%20China%20in%20green%20investments%3B%20deals%20worth%20%242.4%20bn%20completed%20in%20Q3%22%2C%22content%22