.%20This%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20random%20act%20of%20violence%3B%20all%20indications%20are%20that%20it%20was%20a%20premediated%2C%20targeted%20attack.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20full%20investigative%20efforts%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FK3kzC4IbtS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FK3kzC4IbtS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NYPD%20NEWS%20(%40NYPDnews)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNYPDnews%2Fstatus%2F1864706407985221974%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThompson%2C%2050%2C%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20back%20and%20leg%20around%206%3A45%20am%20outside%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Hilton%20Midtown%20hotel%2C%20where%20UnitedHealth%20Group%20Inc.%20was%20hosting%20its%20investor%20day.%20Video%20showed%20the%20attacker%20waiting%20for%20Thompson%20-%20who%20was%20UnitedHealth's%20insurance%20chief%20-%20upon%20his%20arrival%20at%20the%20hotel.%20The%20perpetrator%20approached%20the%20executive%20from%20behind%20and%20shot%20him%20multiple%20times%20before%20leaving%20by%20foot%20and%20then%20riding%20an%20electric%20bike%20toward%20Central%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20UnitedHealth%20had%20a%20security%20team%20at%20the%20hotel%20for%20its%20investor%20day%2C%20it%20didn't%20have%20anyone%20stationed%20outside%20where%20the%20executive%20was%20shot%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20The%20company%20didn't%20comment%20on%20the%20security%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20fell%205.2%25%20Thursday%2C%20erasing%20more%20than%20%2429%20billion%20in%20market%20value.%20The%20stock%20had%20gained%20about%201%25%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20news%20of%20Thompson's%20killing%20broke.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbryan-thompson-unitedhealthcare-quiet-walk-silencer-on-gun-how-unitedhealthcare-ceo-was-murdered-7176331%5C%22%3EQuiet%