e%20Manhattan-based%20museum%20starting%20December%208.%20It%20will%20arrive%20at%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20as%20part%20of%20a%20special%20loan%20from%20Griffin%2C%20who%20purchased%20it%20during%20a%20Sotheby's%20auction%20for%20%2444.6%20million%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommercial%20paleontologist%20Jason%20Cooper%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-finds-dinosaur-skeleton-on-walk-could-get-millions-auction-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20discovered%20Apex%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May%202022%20at%20Morrison%20Formation%20near%20Dinosaur%2C%20Colorado.%20It%20is%2011.5%20feet%20tall%2C%2027%20feet%20long%2C%20and%20nearly%2080%25%20complete.%20Apex%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complete%C2%A0Stegosaurus%C2%A0specimens%20discovered%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESotheby's%2C%20which%20initially%20expected%20the%20fossil%20to%20go%20for%20about%20%246%20million%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Apex%20set%20off%20a%20%26quot%3Bbidding%20battle%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20valuable%20fossil%20ever%20sold%20at%20auction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20some%20paleontologists%20argued%20it%20shouldn't%20have%20been%20privately%20sold%20but%20rather%20used%20for%20educational%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223689%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billionaire%20Ken%20Griffin's%20stegosaurus%20fossil%20on%20display%20at%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20%20on%20December%205%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67522b574adc4cc13434eb89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222438%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fossil%20will%20go%20in%20display%20at%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20on%20December%208%2C%202024.%3Cp%3ETIMOTHY%20A.%20CLARY%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20have%20Apex%20on%20view%20at%20the%20Museum%20and%20grateful%20to%20Ken%20Griffin%20for%20his%20commitment%20to%20sharing%20this%20magnificent%20specimen%20with%20the%20public%20and%20for%20partnering%20with%20our%20Museum%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Sean%20M.%20Decatur%2C%20President%20of%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20release%20said%20Griffin's%20decision%20to%20loan%20the%20fossil%20will%20allow%20scientists%20in%20the%20museum's%C2%A0Division%20of%20Paleontology%C2%A0to%20study%20it%20as%20part%20of%20a%20new%20research%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Griffin%20said%20he%20also%20provided%20sampling%20needed%20for%20scientific%20research%20and%20funding%20for%20educational%20programming.%20A%20postdoctoral%20fellow%20will%20also%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20research%20Apex%20alongside%20other%20Stegosaurus%20specimens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billionaire%20Ken%20Griffin's%20stegosaurus%20fossil%20on%20display%20at%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20%20on%20December%205%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67522b318fb3f94e5073c296%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECitadel%20Ken%20Griffin%20purchased%20the%20fossil%20for%20%2444.6%20million%20in%20July%202024.%3Cp%3ETIMOTHY%20A.%20CLARY%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApex%20offers%20a%20unique%20window%20into%20our%20planet's%20distant%20past%2C%20and%20I'm%20so%20pleased%20to%20partner%20with%20the%20American%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%20to%20showcase%20it%20at%20one%20of%20our%20country's%20preeminent%20scientific%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20Griffin%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20am%20grateful%20that%20millions%20of%2