sn%E2%80%99t%20a%20viable%20solution.%20Sandy%20deduced%20that%20true%20change%20would%20only%20be%20possible%20when%20the%20practice%20of%20non-degradable%20pads%20was%20ousted%20and%20substituted%20with%20eco-friendly%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20we%20introduced%20cloth%20pads.%20These%20can%20be%20reused%20multiple%20times%20after%20washing.%20Economically%20and%20environmentally%2C%20we%20thought%20this%20would%20be%20a%20good%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandy%20informs.%20%E2%80%98Periods%20of%20Pride%E2%80%99%20not%20only%20ushers%20in%20a%20new%20era%20with%20their%20pads%20but%20also%20seeks%20to%20ring%20in%20a%20new%20mindset%20by%20deconstructing%20regressive%20attitudes%20around%20menstruation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Inspired%20by%20the%20women%20in%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20man%20%5BSandy%5D%20walks%20into%20a%20village%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267937%2Fmenstrual-health-period-poverty-delhi-pinkishe-social-impact-facebook-community%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeaks%20to%20its%20women%20about%20periods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20is%20usually%20met%20with%20radio%20silence%20and%20lowered%20gazes.%20So%2C%20when%20that%20man%20can%20say%20that%20he%20has%20influenced%202%2C00%2C000%20teenage%20girls%20and%20women%2C%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20and%20intrigue.%20The%20latter%20is%20because%20one%20would%20wonder%20how%20he%20achieved%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%20describes%20a%20typical%20workshop.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20when%20we%20start%20off%2C%20even%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98period%E2%80%99%20is%20taboo.%20So%2C%20we%20begin%20by%20addressing%20what%20a%20period%20is.%20We%20tell%20girls%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20begun%20menstruating%20by%20what%20age%