s.%20All%20actions%20are%20directed%20towards%20reducing%20carbon%20footprint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20urge%20them%20to%20ask%20their%20parents%20to%20move%20towards%20renewable%20energy%2C%20adopt%20solar%20panels%20and%20thus%20minimise%20their%20electricity%20bill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20mindsets%20is%20palpable%20in%20the%20villages%20where%20Sandy%20has%20carried%20out%20his%20advocacy.%20For%20Sandy%2C%20even%20a%20single%20village%20embracing%20a%20new%20perspective%20on%20menstruation%20through%20his%20workshops%20is%20a%20true%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Ftopic%2Fwater%2Fbrief%2Fmenstrual-health-and-hygiene%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMenstrual%20Health%20and%20Hygiene%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20World%20Bank%2C%20Published%20on%2012%20May%202022.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733377824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D384653%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20surviving%20a%20near-fatal%20accident%2C%20Sandy%20Khanda%20founded%20the%20Green%20Pencil%20Foundation%20to%20tackle%20education%2C%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%20and%20climate%20advocacy.%20His%20%E2%80%98Periods%20of%20Pride%E2%80%99%20initiative%20promotes%20eco-friendly%20menstrual%20products%20and%20has%20impacted%20over%20two%20lakh%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F384653%2Fsandy-khanda-menstrual-hygiene-green-pencil-foundation-climate-change%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%2