-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewood%20strand%20composition%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadds%20a%20subtle%20texture%20to%20the%20overall%20monochromatic%2C%20industrial-themed%20office%20space.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20OSB%20does%20manage%20to%20lend%20some%20bespoke%20detailing%20to%20the%20building%2C%20it%20is%20susceptible%20to%20moisture%20absorption.%20This%2C%20says%20Aameer%2C%20can%20affect%20its%20dimensional%20stability%20and%20performance%20over%20time.%20Another%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20since%20OSB%20is%20procured%20from%20trees%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverify%20the%20specific%20environmental%20certifications%20and%20sustainability%20attributes%20of%20the%20OSB%20product%20being%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Compressed%20Stabilised%20Earth%20Bricks%20(CSEB)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20study%20underscored%2C%20%E2%80%9CCompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%20due%20to%20the%20lower%20amount%20of%20energy%20required%20for%20their%20production%2C%20lower%20cost%20and%20lower%20carbon%20footprint.%20Compared%20to%20cement%20concrete%2C%20CSEBs%20also%20require%20less%20embodied%20energy%2C%20with%20some%20authors%20indicating%20that%20only%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20production%20energy%20of%20cement%20concrete%20is%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20architects%20Rahul%20Kadri%2C%20Nithin%20Hosabettu%2C%20Sahil%20Bipin%20Deshpande%2C%20Viraj%20Naralkar%2C%20and%20Aakash%20Shrivastav%20of%20Mumbai-based%20IMK%20Architects%20were%20tasked%20with%20designing%20the%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%2C%20using