arbitrator%20as%20a%20private%20judge%20who%20ensures%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20resolution%20without%20involving%20the%20formal%20court%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%20works%20well%20for%20commercial%2C%20contractual%2C%20financial%2C%20intellectual%20property%2C%20and%20even%20international%20disputes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-500x561.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-500x561.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-267x300.jpeg%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-768x862.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087-150x168.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-02-at-5.05.09-PM-1733283087.jpeg%201140w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20G%20Abhishek%2C%20a%20lawyer%20handling%20Supreme%20Court%20SLP%20cases%2C%20explains%20that%20ADR%20processes%20almost%20resemble%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20system.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CArbitration%20benefits%20courts%20by%20addressing%20less%20critical%20issues%20outside%20the%20courtroom%2C%20saving%20judicial%20time%20for%20more%20pressing%20cases.%20Consumers%20also%20gain%20quick%20and%20quality%20resolutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20advantages%20have%20prompted%20legislative%20reforms%20aimed%20at%20making%20arbitration%20more%20accessible%20and%20efficient%20in%20India.%20The%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202019%20seeks%20to%20transform%20the%20country%20into%20a%20more%20arbitration-friendly%20jurisdiction.%20By%20reducing%20court%20involvement%20and%20aligning%20Indian%20arbitration%20laws%20with%20international%20standards%2C%20the%20Act%20aims%20to%20create%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20predictable%20legal%20framework%20for%20resolving%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20characteristics%20of%20arbitration%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Voluntary%20agreement%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArbitration%20typically%20stems%20from%20mutual%20consent%2C%20outlined%20in%20contracts%20that%20bind%20parties%20to%20settle%20disputes%20through%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Neutral%20arbitrator%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20third%20party%20%E2%80%94%20often%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20dispute%E2%80%99s%20subject%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20acts%20as%20an%20impartial%20decision-maker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Private%20and%20confidential%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20Unlike%20court%20proceedings%2C%20arbitration%20is%20confidential%20and%20takes%20place%20in%20an%20arbitration%20centre%20which%20protects%20sensitive%20information%20and%20preserves%20business%20reputations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Binding%20decisions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20arbitrator%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20called%20an%20award%2C%20is%20usually%20final%20and%20enforceable%2C%20with%20limited%20grounds%20for%20appeal.%20This%20ensures%20a%20conclusive%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Flexibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Parties%20can%20tailor%20the%20process%2C%20including%20selecting%20arbitrators%2C%20and%20setting%20rules%20and%20timelines%2C%20making%20it%20faster%20and%20more%20adaptable%20than%20litigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Cost-effective%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arbitration%20often%20reduces%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20prolonged%20court%20battles%2C%20as%20the%20process%20is%20streamlined%20with%20fewer%20procedural%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20International%20applicability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arbitration%20is%20widely%20recognised%20across%20borders%20through%20treaties%20like%20the%20New%20York%20Convention%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20resolving%20international%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20solve%20disputes%20via%20arbitration%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnybody%20who%20has%20mentioned%20in%20the%20agreement%20clause%20that%20their%20disputes%20will%20be%20solved%20via%20arbitration%20can%20approach%20the%20arbitration%20centres.%20The%20agreement%20must%20be%20submitted%20as%20proof%20for%20further%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20parties%20have%20not%20included%20an%20arbitration%20clause%20in%20their%20agreement%2C%20they%20can%20submit%20an%20application%20to%20the%20court%20under%20Section%2011%20of%20the%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%20(1996)%2C%20requesting%20to%20fix%20an%20arbitration.%20Based%20on%20the%20technicalities%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20retired%20judge%20or%20anyone%20with%20equal%20expertise%20will%20be%20appointed%20as%20the%20arbitrator%20for%20the%20dispute%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%2