2C%20healthy%20options%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20store%20and%20distribute%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20This%20pragmatic%20approach%20underscores%20her%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20elderly%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20daily%20requirements%20are%20met%20with%20thoughtful%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20her%20family%20initially%20struggled%20to%20understand%20her%20work%2C%20Aparna%E2%80%99s%20husband%20has%20since%20become%20one%20of%20her%20greatest%20supporters.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20used%20to%20ask%20me%20where%20I%20was%20going%2C%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%20but%20now%20he%20understands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%20His%20support%2C%20alongside%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%2C%20has%20been%20crucial%20in%20helping%20Aparna%20balance%20her%20social%20work%20with%20family%20responsibilities.%20%E2%80%9CTime%20management%20is%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20constant%20juggling%20act%20between%20her%20duties%20at%20home%20and%20her%20work%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAparna%E2%80%99s%20journey%20has%20not%20been%20without%20its%20challenges.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20she%20encountered%20resistance%20from%20some%20NGOs%20where%20she%20noticed%20that%20children%20were%20not%20being%20properly%20cared%20for.%20Instead%20of%20ignoring%20the%20issue%2C%20she%20took%20action.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20that%20some%20NGOs%20weren%E2%80%99t%20meeting%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stand%20by.%20I%20spoke%20directly%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20insisting%20they%20prioritise%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20well-being%2C%20ensure%20proper%20care%2C%20and%20meet%20their%20basic%20needs%2C%20including%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20highlighting%20her%20commitment%20to%20advocating%20for%20the%20vulnerable%2C%20even%20in%20difficult%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiring%20the%20next%20generation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3